<th colspan="2" class="fn summary" style="background-color:gold; font-size:120%;"><i>Fourteen Holy Helpers</i></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center;">
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Fourteen_helpers_.jpg" class="image" title="Fourteen helpers .jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/81/Fourteen_helpers_.jpg/200px-Fourteen_helpers_.jpg" width="200" height="280" border="0" /></a></div>
